<div type="abstract"><head>Offener Brief des Rates</head><p>Der Rat verkündet die Freundschaft mit Ulrich Ainkorn nach Herausgabe des von Fritz Zütsch, Bürger zu Nürnberg, geraubten Gelds.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_528" id="263v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_528_line_1576347494114_3191">VVir ~ die <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> des <expan>R<ex>ats</ex></expan> der Stat cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>Bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc daʒ für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l21">vns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> iſt 
<del rend="strikethrough">Stephan </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_528_r1l20">fricʒ </ab></add> CƷütſchn vnſer <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vnd hat vns <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l22">vvie Jm Vlrich Ainkorn etvvieuil gelts genomen het / das Er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l23">Jm gencʒlich <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab / Als vns der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l24">vnd auch <expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / daʒ vvir darümb / 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l25">Ainkorns freund <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd alſo <expan>vverde<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l26"><expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Ainkorns vnd auch aller der die darunter verdaht ſind </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l27">gut freunde v̈mb dıe tat <expan>ongeu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_528" id="263v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> des <expan>r<ex>ats</ex></expan> der stat czu
                <expan>Nür<ex>emberg,</ex></expan>
<expan>bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc., daz für uns <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist
              <add>Fricz</add> Czütschn, unser <expan>b<ex>urger,</ex></expan> und hat uns
                <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>, wie im Ulrich Ainkorn etwievil gelts genomen het,
            das er im genczlich <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab, als uns der
                <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> gesagt und auch <expan>gebete<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, daz
            wir darümb des <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Ainkorns freund
              <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan>; und also <expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Ainkorns und auch aller der, die darunter verdaht sind,
            gut freunde ümb die tat <expan>on gev<ex>er</ex>de.</expan> Mit
              <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
